There is some type of hypnosis machine that takes you to (based on the clothes and the design of the club/studio) Mumbai in the year 2056. Everyone signs up for this experience as they see the advertisement ( song teaser) as at the end the other person is in the hypnosis room instead of Hassan Raheem.

snippet.textDisplay:
My personal ranking till now 😬. Share yours as I would like to see what others think:

1- Jhol
2- Turri Jandi
3- O Yaara
4- Harkalay
5- Aayi Aayi
6- Maghron La
7- Chal Chaliye
8- 2AM
9- Blockbuster

There were quite a few songs which sounded meh at first but once you listen, they grow on you and you start to appreciate the subtle nuances, when you go through BTS then they become mind blowing. With Jhol and now Turri Jandi, the season is in fifth gear right now 🔥🔥🔥
